{"tid":2089164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭若驊：國安人員並非冇王管  受國家監察機關監督","createTime":"2020-07-01T13:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T14:13:36.000Z","uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b6509c20ca00fa70b79eec7e64c84a2e77232551","tid":2089164,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:55:12.000Z","msg":"《港區國安法》條文訂明駐港國安機構人員執行職務時，不受香港法律及法院管轄，人員及車輛亦不受截查；法例亦指明，維護國家安全委員會的決定，不受司法覆核制衡。<br />\n<br />\n被問及如果國安公署人員違法，由誰管轄，鄭若驊僅重申，<strong>條文第 50 條訂明維護國家安全公署應當「嚴格依法履行職責」，「依法接受監督」</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不得侵害任何個人和組織的合法權益；鄭若驊表示，有關人員執法時，要注意有無違反相關原則，並會受國家監察機關監督，<strong>「希望你（記者）會理解個情況」，「呢個法律的實際操作情況，我們要咁理解。」</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/林鄭/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%2F&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9UBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=4104963b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%2F&h=e8ac0d61\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/林鄭/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n===<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF-SKS89xxRg&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9UBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=2645888e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg</a>"},{"pid":"678fb845b9eb649bd94209d7f7b74cfcd4cce5c3","tid":2089164,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"習近平 = 王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b6e1db210d7f230d8a937deac39b355f485ff1","tid":2089164,"uid":237465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:56:29.000Z","msg":"又係度搞笑嗎 ?   32000 名恐怖分子都無皇管啦 ! 更何況 升級人士"},{"pid":"2e11c4f088d9483bb28a7f7eecf4d0